<bibRefCitation author="Litvaitis" pageId="8" pageNumber="503" refString="Litvaitis, M. K., Bolanos, D. M. &amp; Quiroga, S. Y. (2010) When names are wrong and colours deceive: unraveling the Pseudoceros bicolor species complex (Turbellaria: Polycladida). Journal of Natural History, 44, 829 - 845. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222930903537074" type="journal article" year="2010">
